<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently the mysqli adapter doesn't take in to consideration the mysqli options that can be passed in (<a href="http://us2.php.net/manual/en/mysqli.options.php">http://us2.php.net/manual/en/mysqli.options.php</a>).</p>

<p>I feel this can be best achieved using the driver_options variable and modifying the _connect() method to handle if there are any driver_options.</p>

